request.description:
List of accounts with details.


Sample request:

    {
        "header": {
            "ID": "(uuid)",
            "application": "598A4414-395A-43D6-A9C3-D53A15E6E9F6"
        },
        "payload": {
            "ownAccounts": true,
            "userId": "123456"
        }
    }

NBG Account beneficiaries masked.

Sample request:

    {
        "header": {
            "ID": "(uuid)",
            "application": "598A4414-395A-43D6-A9C3-D53A15E6E9F6"
        },
        "payload": {
            "iban": "GR1601100400000004012345678",
            "userId": "123456"
        }
    }

List of my accounts in foreign currency with details.

Sample request:

    {
        "header": {
            "ID": "(uuid)",
            "application": "598A4414-395A-43D6-A9C3-D53A15E6E9F6"
        },
        "payload": {
            "ownAccounts": true,
            "userId": "123456"
        }
    }

